#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/telemetry-opentracing-to-otel-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Migrate from OpenTracing to OpenTelemetry tracing"
msgstr "Migrar do OpenTracing para o rastreamento OpenTelemetry"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/telemetry-opentracing-to-otel-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Migrate an application from https://docs.quarkiverse.io/quarkus-smallrye-opentracing/dev/index.html[OpenTracing] to xref:opentelemetry.adoc[OpenTelemetry tracing] in Quarkus 3.x."
msgstr "Migre uma aplicação do https://docs.quarkiverse.io/quarkus-smallrye-opentracing/dev/index.html[OpenTracing] para o xref:opentelemetry.adoc[rastreamento OpenTelemetry] no Quarkus 3.x."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/telemetry-opentracing-to-otel-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The legacy OpenTracing framework has been deprecated in favor of the new OpenTelemetry tracing framework. We announced the https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-observability-roadmap-2023/#opentracing-archived[OpenTracing deprecation on November 2022], and we are dropping the extension from Quarkus core repository and moving it to the Quarkiverse Hub."
msgstr "O framework OpenTracing legado foi descontinuado em favor do novo framework de rastreamento OpenTelemetry. Nós anunciamos a https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-observability-roadmap-2023/#opentracing-archived[descontinuação do OpenTracing em novembro de 2022], e estamos removendo a extensão do repositório core do Quarkus e movendo-a para o Quarkiverse Hub."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/telemetry-opentracing-to-otel-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It is now time to migrate your application to OpenTelemetry tracing if you haven’t done it yet."
msgstr "Chegou a hora de migrar sua aplicação para o rastreamento OpenTelemetry, se ainda não o fez."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/telemetry-opentracing-to-otel-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you need to migrate from Quarkus 2.16.x please beware that configuration properties are different and you should check the older Quarkus OpenTelemetry guide version, https://quarkus.io/version/2.16/guides/opentelemetry#configuration-reference[here]."
msgstr "Se você precisar migrar do Quarkus 2.16.x, esteja ciente de que as propriedades de configuração são diferentes e você deve verificar a versão mais antiga do guia Quarkus OpenTelemetry, https://quarkus.io/version/2.16/guides/opentelemetry#configuration-reference[aqui]."

